name: AOM
description: AOM is an important component of DFBTC's cross-chain revenue, which is generated by the technology to solve the zero-interest assets of Bitcoin. DFBTC anchors BTC in the ETH network through cross-chain anchoring technology, providing higher liquidity. In the future, AOM will create more ways to generate income from high-quality assets, and in the later stage, it will cross-chain to other high-quality main chains to provide greater value.
